LOCATION:SIDNEY AND LOIS ESKENAZI MUSEUM OF ART - Room Number: Check in a
 t the information desk on the first floor
SUMMARY:Exploring Twins in Art
DESCRIPTION:Discover stories of legendary twins\, like Heracles\, Osiris\
 , and the Mayan Hero twins\, as you explore the history of twins in diffe
 rent cultures. Also explore parts of the world where twins occur twice as
  often as in the United States and the traditions and artifacts surroundi
 ng this phenomenon.  Know Before You GoSpace is available for the first 1
 2 people to check in with Guest Services on the day. Drop by the informat
 ion desk on the first floor of the museum when you arrive.Strollers are w
 elcome. A small handbag may be carried at your side. Backpacks and large 
 bags will need to be stored before touring. Learn more aboutmuseum guidel
 ines.If you park in the Indiana Memorial Union parking lot\, Guest Servic
 es can validate your parking voucher for a discount.Read aboutwhere to fi
 nd us and where to park\,
