 closely at artworkŌĆöasking what we see\, think\, feel\, and wonder. Toge
 ther\, we'll explore the artist's possible message and its social meaning
 \, then turn those reflections into our own creative responses.</p><p>  W
 hether you're a writer or simply curious to try something new\, you'll fi
 nd inspiration here and a welcoming community to share the journey.</p><h
 3>  What to Bring</h3><ul><li>your favorite pencil (no pens).  </li><li>a
  notebook or paper. Clipboards are available to borrow.  </li><li>a phone
  or camera to take a picture of the art for later reference.  </li></ul><
