 elief sculpture on a provided "scratch block." Leading the carving worksh
 op are Sculpture Trails Outdoor Museum staff Laura Gonzalez (Outreach Coo
 rdinator) and Ethan Harmon (Artist-in-Residence)\, as well as Eskenazi Mu
 seum of Art's resident Arts-based Wellness Experiences Manager\, Keaton E
 vans-Black.</span></p><p><span data-ogsc="" data-ogsb="white">PLEASE NOTE
