 e museum with separate parallel programming that supports creativity\, an
 d relaxation. Kids will have the opportunity to engage with art while par
 ents relax with a variety of activities.  K-12 Children's Program12:00ŌĆō
 12:30 PM: Guided gallery exploration.  12:30ŌĆō2:00 PM: Hands-on art acti
 vity in the art studio + snack.  Adult Program12:00ŌĆō1:00 PM: Experience
  select galleries through a fun and casual guided experience.  1:00ŌĆō2:0
 0 PM: Choose your own adventure: relax with art-filled coloring sheets\, 
 have a snack from the museum cafe or explore more of the galleries at you
 r leisure.
